Charles Le Moyne (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Le_Moyne_(actor) 0 Charles Le Moyne (June 27, 1880 – September 13, 1956) was an American motion picture actor of the silent era. He appeared in 73 films between 1915 and 1937. Charles_Le_Moyne ( June_27 , 1880 – September_13_,_1956 ) was an_American_motion_picture_actor of the_silent_era .
